HowTo:
	Compile: 
		1. cd pelican
		2. make html
	View:
		1. compile site
		2. make serve
		3. visit localhost:8000 in your web browser
	Add a news item:
		1. cd pelican/news
		2. copy an existing YYYYMMDD.md file and rename with date of item
		3. update the meta data fields at top of new file
		4. add content to file, emulate markdown formatting from previous items
		5. compile and view


Python Dependencies (install with pip, virtualenv is your friend):
	pelican
	Markdown 


Resources:
	https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/Markdown-Cheatsheet
	http://docs.getpelican.com/en/3.3.0/
	https://github.com/DandyDev/pelican-bootstrap3
